STATUS MACHINE (client-side, driven by server room.status):

'home'
  ↓ createRoom() or joinRoom()
'lobby'          ← room.status = "waiting"
  ↓ host clicks "ESCOLHER MODO" (min 3 players)
'modeSelect'     ← local state only (no server change)
  ↓ host selects mode
'submodeSelect'  ← only for palavraSecreta
